textAfterTable: Bang for the buck I am from Hillview (Bullitt County, KY) and I still pay the in-state tuition charge for IN! It's a great value and a whole lot cheaper than the Louisville schools. It takes about 25 minutes to get to class, and parking isn't too bad if you hit it just right. Am enjoying being here I have been generally accepted by all - teachers, classmates, school staff. I am a 42 yr old returning student and fit in just like I was 22. Am learning a lot I have been challenged by the teachers and professors. The classes are very interesting and a lot more fun than 15 yrs ago!!
